Web Grilo Player
================

Project in a very early stage.

Main idea: Desktop application developed in HTML using WebKitGTK+ [1]_ to play
multimedia content provided by Grilo [2]_.


Requirements
------------

*Web Grilo Player* depends on:

* GTK+ (``gtk+-2.0``)
* WebKitGTK+ (``webkit-1.0``)
* Grilo (``grilo-0.1``)
* Tango icon theme (``tango-icon-theme``)
* jQuery UI (``libjs-jquery-ui``)


Installation
------------

See the ``INSTALL`` file.


Availability
------------

The cutting-edge version of this project is always available from the Git
repository at http://gitorious.org/web-grilo-player/.


